features: 【STURDY MATERIAL】Office chair headrest is made of sponge + 3D fiber mesh, it is soft, can effectively cushion and absorb pressure. Its back as well as the support rod is made of plastic material, featuring high strength, durable.

【ADJUSTABLE HEIGHT AND ANGLE】It's a new design headrest pillow for most kinds of office chair, makes your chair more comfortable. The height of the headrest can be adjusted, and the height can be increased by about 4cm/1.57inch. You can adjust as needed.

【NECK PROTECTION】The heightened accessory of the office computer chair is ergonomically designed, makes your chair more comfortable, and protects your neck and spine. With the computer chair headrest, you can sit up straight and feel comfortable, which can help you relieve neck pain effectively.

【NO PUNCHING】The chair headrest attachment equipped with screw bag, no punching design, easy to install. You only need to hang the chair headrest on the office chair, after adjusting the angle, turn the screw to fix it tightly. The fixing clip is thickened and deepened and the mounting holes are reinforced, making the headrest more stable.

【3 SIZES OF FIXING CLIP】The office chair back has 3 different fixing clip sizes for you to choose. Their inner diameters are about 2.2cm/0.87inch, 2.6cm/1.02inch, 3cm/1.18inch, please confirm the size of the seat back before purchasing.
